
--------------------------------------------------------------------HOW TO PLAY---------------------------------------------------------------------

First scene that should be loaded: startscene

Objective = collect all computer chips on the level (there are 4 per level), then go to portal to be transported to the next level
			collect as many coins as you can

Player controls/movements: 
	move left = A or left arrow key
	move right = D or right arrow key
	Jump = space bar
	shoot = left click on mouse
	Wall jump = jump on one wall then move to the other wall and hit jump again



